videos.description: Sacar Anim anticipiates Nate Fowler's pass and takes it the other way, finishing with a smooth finger roll on the fast break.
videos.headline: Anim steals and scores for Marquette

videos.description: Aaron Thompson drives and kicks to Sean McDermott, who drains a triple despite the contact to earn himself a 4-point play.
videos.headline: McDermott connects for 4-point play

videos.description: Markus Howard gets by Kamar Baldwin and connects on an off-balance pull-up jumper as the shot clock expires, giving Marquette a 32-23 lead over Butler.
videos.headline: Marquette's Howard hits circus shot to beat shot clock
